{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "圣树 第20章 6-1 契约的真相",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "奈迪犹的目的是打败封印巴哈姆特、\\n创造虚伪世界的元凶并把真相公之于众。\\n塞西娅得知被篡改的部分历史真相后，\\n认为奈迪犹所言属实\\n便答应为其解除结界。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "龙鳞病以迅雷不及掩耳之势\\n侵蚀了新生儿的身体，\\n不久他便离开了这个世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "他的替身随后问世，\\n神不知鬼不觉地进行了掉包。\\n而他的尸骨，则被精灵接收。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "他的魂魄化为魔力，\\n肉身则被用于\\n龙化的研究而消失。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这本应是那个婴儿，也就是……\\n我短暂的一生。然而——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "意识还很模糊的我，在自我\\n与他人的边界十分暧昧的世界里，\\n被不知何人所呼唤。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "然后在一片混沌中，\\n我遵从本能进行了回应。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "就这样，我复活了。\\n同时，也能感觉到有“东西”\\n潜伏在我的身体里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "很久以后我才得知，\\n那个所谓的“东西”\\n就是巴哈姆特。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你是说你借助\\n巴哈姆特的力量复活了吗？\\n那么，龙鳞病……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我的身体充满了龙之力后，\\n龙鳞病的症状转眼就消失了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "但是捡回了一条命的我\\n在人类世界已经没有容身之处，\\n只能在精灵国长大。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这就是我的成长经历……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我不理解……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "也就是说你是在\\n连话都不会说的时候\\n和龙缔结了契约吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "龙只会和认可其力量之人\\n缔结契约。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "无法想象龙会和一个\\n刚出生不久的小毛孩\\n缔结契约。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这对巴哈姆特来说\\n应该是一个不得已的选择。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "长久以来被封印在异界的\\n创世之龙，为了回到人世间\\n正在寻找宿主。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "恰好在那时发现了\\n游离于世界之外的我，\\n这个继承了龙之血的容器。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "为了得到我这个\\n即将化为魔力的容器，\\n才勉强认可了这份契约。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "那么，你那时之所以\\n摄入魔力是因为……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "这是不平等契约的代价。\\n巴哈姆特的力量对于\\n尚且年幼的我来说过于强大。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我的外貌因为遭到龙之力侵蚀\\n而发生了变化。并且时至今日我自身的\\n魔力也依然不断被巴哈姆特夺走。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "如果不从外界摄入魔力，\\n我的身体就会被巴哈姆特之力\\n所侵蚀，立即枯朽。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "这就是你必须\\n要摄入魔力的理由……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "是我的父亲芬罗达\\n让奈迪犹的身体\\n变得可以补充魔力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "他发现本已成为实验牺牲品的\\n孩子复活后，立即试图为他续命，\\n还真符合他反复无常的作风。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "无论如何，多亏了他\\n奈迪犹才捡回一条命，\\n这也是不可否认的事实……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "奈迪犹，你为什么想重新\\n和巴哈姆特缔结契约？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "不断吸取力量的巴哈姆特\\n对你来说应该是\\n碍事的存在才对。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我……比任何人都清楚\\n潜伏在我体内的龙\\n拥有深不见底的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "正因为如此，\\n我才决定要利用他的力量，\\n而不是将其抹杀。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我要将巴哈姆特\\n对“封印了自身的存在”的\\n那股愤怒为我所用。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "封印了巴哈姆特的\\n和我想毁灭的对象\\n是同一个存在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "同时也是制造出了\\n这个虚假世界的存在。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "制造出了\\n这个虚假世界的存在？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你是说这个世界的历史\\n是被人蓄意篡改的吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "伊莉雅教的真相和魔神的诞生……\\n不，或许就连哥哥的事也……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我一时间很难相信\\n有谁能策划出\\n如此大规模的阴谋。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "总有一天我们会知道的。\\n而曝光其真面目\\n也是我的使命。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "我要打倒那个存在，\\n揭开笼罩这个世界的虚伪，\\n将真相公之于众。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "为此我需要重新\\n和巴哈姆特缔结契约，\\n使其无与伦比的力量为我所用。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "塞西娅，我请求你\\n解除这个结界，\\n助我一臂之力——",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "你伤害了哥哥和巴尔库斯哥哥，\\n我绝对不会原谅你。\\n但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "自那以后，\\n我看待这个世界的角度\\n就与从前不同了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "自从那时……\\n和她共同行动过后……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我就没法把你说的话\\n当成信口拈来的谎言……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "现在——为了解除这个结界，\\n就让我来献上祈祷吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "塞西娅，你终于做出决断了啊。\\n感谢你愿意帮忙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "请不要会错意……\\n我并没有百分之百\\n信任你们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "奈迪犹，芩罗达，\\n我还需要对你们\\n进一步进行观察。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "还有奈迪犹，\\n我对你有一个要求。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "希望你对哥哥的态度不要\\n那么恶劣，而是把你知道的事\\n都告诉他，跟他进行沟通。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "哥哥他也有自己的想法。\\n那是哥哥和所有的同伴\\n都坚信的伟大理想和信念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我希望你也能\\n倾听哥哥的故事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100039_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奈迪犹",
            "context": "知道了……我答应你。\\n前提是还有机会\\n和那个男人碰面的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "呵呵，看来你们谈妥了呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100048_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "芩罗达",
            "context": "奈迪犹，我要离开一下。\\n因为似乎有必要\\n稍微争取一下时间了呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "巴尔库斯哥哥……\\n请原谅我自作主张。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "你不需要道歉，\\n这是你做出的决断。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100016_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "巴尔库斯",
            "context": "我也会和你一同前往顶端\\n看清他的想法，\\n判断他的是非对错。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_20_09_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
